== Mellon's tax cuts ==

The recent edits re the Mellon tax cuts seem to be to be rather laudatory.  I have some doubts a Keynesian would concur with the characterization of the tax cuts as jump starting the economy. I wonder if this is completely balanced?--[[User:Wehwalt|Wehwalt]] ([[User talk:Wehwalt|talk]]) 00:06, 23 June 2016 (UTC)
